SPI Holding Inc, a group consisting ofHicks and Haas and Acadia Partners LP, said it has receivedcommitments for the senior bank financing needed to completeits proposed acquisition of Spectradyne Inc for 46 dlrs a sharein cash or securities, or a total of about 452 mln dlrs.    The transaction was conditioned on the arrangement fofinancing by today.    It said it has also executed multi-year employment andnon-competition agreements with five Spectrayne senior managers. Reuter&#3;